q_en: Which warehouse has more Cotton Fabric between the main and auxiliary warehouses?

steps.sql:
SELECT c.customer_name
FROM customers c
JOIN orders o ON c.id = o.user_id
JOIN order_product op ON o.id = op.order_id
JOIN products p ON op.product_id = p.id
JOIN products_types pt ON p.products_type_id = pt.id
WHERE pt.description = 'Casual Wear';
steps.description: To find the customer who placed an order for the product with the product type description 'Casual Wear', we need to join multiple tables to retrieve the required information.
